abstract: Stocks end best week of year, helped by big gains by retailers and technology firms.
lead_paragraph: Shares of Nike and Alphabet were up, and the market was headed toward its best week in more than a year.

headline.main: Modest Advance for Market as Retail and Tech Stocks Rise
headline.print_headline: Retailers Help Market Close Year’s Strongest Week

snippet: Shares of Nike and Alphabet were up, and the market was headed toward its best week in more than a year.
